This paper deals with explaining and regularizing neural networks, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions image classification datasets, indicating a possible connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of trust and security in critical applications, suggesting a potential overlap with cryptography and security (cs.CR).
